title: Film blowing machine US-SJ-A50-700
title_uz: Polietilen rulonli plyonka ishlab chiqaruvchi ekstruder US-SJ-A50-700
title_ru: Экструдер для изготовления рулонной полиэтиленовой пленки US-SJ-A50-700
short_description: This US-SJ-A50-700 extruder, which produces 35 kg of polyethylene roll film per hour, has a main motor power of 11 kW and a total power of 24 kW. The maximum width of the produced film is 600 mm. The total weight of the extruder equipment is 2.4 tons. Its dimensions are 3000*2500*3800 mm. The description below also shows other models of this equipment. Their parameters and prices differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Soatiga 35 kg polietilen rulonli plyonka ishlab chiqaruvchi ushbu US-SJ-A50-700 ekstruderning asosiy motor quvvati 11 kW, umumiy quvvati esa 24 kW ni tashkil qiladi. Ishlab chiqariluvchi plyonkaning maksimal kengligi 600 mm dan iborat. Ekstruder uskunasining umumiy vazni 2.4 tonna. O'lchamlari esa 3000*2500*3800 mm. Quyidagi tavsifda ushbu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham aks etgan. Ularning parametr va narxlari bir-biridan farq qiladi.
